channel.title: Problem With Added Models
channel.description:
Ok, so every time I add models into my client, they end up going behind the character so that I can't see them if they're directly in front of the character. It's hard to explain, so here's some pictures.
[IMG]http://i328.photobucket.com/albums/l356/Dyz323/Problem1.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i328.photobucket.com/albums/l356/Dyz323/Problem2.jpg[/img]
But I know they're not in the wrong place (except for the battle axe being a little too far down) because they look fine from the front.
[IMG]http://i328.photobucket.com/albums/l356/Dyz323/Problem3.jpg[/img]
So yeah, if anyone could help me out that would be great :) I think I remember dealing with this in the past, I just don't remember how I fixed it.
